---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact — Wychwood Partners" description="Book a call to pressure-test execution discipline.">
  <main class="shell py-14">
    <h1>Book an Intro Call</h1>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      If you’re a founder, investor, or board member dealing with margin drift, weak cash visibility, stalled integration, or growth that feels less controlled than it should, you can book a short introductory conversation below.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      Include stage, ownership structure, urgency, and the specific constraint you’re trying to resolve. If it’s a fit, we’ll schedule a call. If it isn’t, I’ll say so.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Email</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          hello@wychwood-partners.com
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/seanfoy/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text))] hover:underline"
        >
          Connect on LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Direct booking</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          If a conversation would be useful, you can schedule a time directly.
        </p>

        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/RRKFf2z6rNDrmzFE8"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] bg-[rgb(var(--brand-anchor))] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:opacity-95"
        >
          Book an Intro Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-12 max-w-3xl text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      Experience across venture-backed growth, private equity hold periods, multi-country scale, and IPO environments.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
